<plot>SILENCIO (Silence) takes us into the mind of Marta, a paranoid schizophrenic who is struggling to live a normal life. Marta is literally haunted by her past, in the form of herself-10 years younger. She finds refuge in the home of a friendly old man and thinks she has finally found her place in the world. Her "other-self" disagrees.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?496865</url></doc>
